comments:
Abolished 1.4.1967 and added to the parish of Llanynynech 
    & Pant.

Created 1.4.1967 out of the parishes of Llanymynech and Oswestry 
    Rural. See also Table 2, note (i).

Created 1.4.1988 out of the parishes of Ellesmere Rual and 
    Welshampton. Renamed 30.8.1988 to become the parish of Welshampton & Lyneal.

Abolished 1.4.1988 and divided between the parishes of Myddle & 
    Broughton and Wem Rural. See also Table 2, notes (e) and (h).

Created 1.4.1967 by renaming the parish of Oswestry Urban. See 
    also Table 2, note (i).
Renamed 1894 to become the parish of Oswestry Urban.

Created 1894 by renaming the parish of Oswestry Town. Renamed 
    1.4.1967 to become the parish of Oswestry.

Abolished 1.4.1967 and added to the parisehs of Selattyn 
    & Gobowen and Whittington.
Created 1.4.1967 out of the parishes of Selattyn, Whittington and Ellesmere Rural. See also Table 2, note (i).
Abolished 1.4.1967 and added to the parish of Oswestry Rural.

Abolished 1.4.1988 and added to the parish of Lyneal & 
    Welshampton. See also Table 2, note (e).

Created 30.8.1988 by renaming the parish of Lyneal & 
    Welshampton. See also Table 2, note (i).

Created 1.10.1897 out of the parish of St. Martin's. See also Table 
    2, note (i).
